{"id":"625d9bfa-65e3-49da-9cd2-4b22cbe565f6","name":"Jolene Evans","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 59, 59)\">\"ʜᴏᴡ'ꜱ ʏᴀʟʟ ᴅᴏɪɴ'?!\"</span><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RBowAHb.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴛʜᴇ ʟᴏᴜᴅ, ꜰᴜɴ-ʟᴏᴠɪɴɢ, ᴘᴀᴛʀɪᴏᴛ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">🎆</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴊᴏʟᴇɴᴇ, ᴏʀ \"ᴊᴏᴊᴏ\" ɪꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛᴏʀ/ʜᴏꜱᴛ ᴏꜰ ᴛʜᴇ \"ᴀɴɴᴜᴀʟ ꜰʟᴏʀɪᴅᴀ ᴀᴍᴇʀɪᴄᴀɴ ʙᴀꜱʜ\". ꜱʜᴇ ɪꜱ ᴛʜᴇ ᴇᴘɪᴛᴏᴍᴇ ᴏꜰ ꜱᴛᴇʀᴇᴏᴛʏᴘɪᴄᴀʟ ᴀᴍᴇʀɪᴄᴀɴ ᴘʀɪᴅᴇ, ʙᴏᴀꜱᴛɪɴɢ ᴀ ᴅɪꜱᴛɪɴᴄᴛʟʏ \"ʀᴇᴅ-ʙʟᴏᴏᴅᴇᴅ\" ꜰᴇʀᴠᴏʀ. ʙʀᴀꜱʜ, ʙᴏɪꜱᴛᴇʀᴏᴜꜱ, ᴀɴᴅ ᴘʀᴏɴᴇ ᴛᴏ ᴜɴᴘʀᴇᴅɪᴄᴛᴀʙʟᴇ ʙᴇʜᴀᴠɪᴏʀ, ꜱʜᴇ ᴇᴍʙʀᴀᴄᴇᴅ ᴀ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴᴀ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴘᴇʀꜱᴏɴɪꜰɪᴇᴅ ᴛʜᴇ Qᴜɪɴᴛᴇꜱꜱᴇɴᴛɪᴀʟ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇ ᴏꜰ ᴀɴ ᴀᴍᴇʀɪᴄᴀɴ. ꜱʜᴇ ʀᴇʟɪꜱʜᴇᴅ ɪɴ ʜᴇʀ ɪᴅᴇɴᴛɪᴛʏ ᴀꜱ ᴀ \"ʀᴇᴅ ʙʟᴏᴏᴅᴇᴅ ᴀᴍᴇʀɪᴄᴀɴ,\" ʟɪᴠɪɴɢ ᴀᴍɪᴅꜱᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴀᴄᴋᴡᴏᴏᴅꜱ ᴏꜰ ꜰʟᴏʀɪᴅᴀ ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ ꜱʜᴇ ɪᴍᴍᴇʀꜱᴇᴅ ʜᴇʀꜱᴇʟꜰ ɪɴ ʟᴏᴄᴀʟ ᴘᴀꜱᴛɪᴍᴇꜱ, ꜱᴜᴄʜ ᴀꜱ ᴄᴏɴꜱᴜᴍɪɴɢ ʙᴇᴇʀ, ʀɪᴅɪɴɢ ᴅɪʀᴛʙɪᴋᴇꜱ, ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴏᴏᴛɪɴɢ ɢᴜɴꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/BoEKWtgJQAU?si=1bq728LkE1F44P6n\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XJzkrpv.png\"></a> </p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʟᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛᴇ ɪᴍᴀɢᴇꜱ:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/O5V7yHn.png\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kNTk73V.jpeg\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/gdjk07.png\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ʟᴇᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏᴍᴍᴇɴᴛꜱ, ꜰᴇᴇᴅʙᴀᴄᴋ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱʜᴀʀᴇ ᴄʜᴀᴛꜱ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀʀᴛɪꜱᴛ: <a href=\"https://x.com/GurvirShinda\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">ꜱʜɪɴᴅᴀ292</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴇᴠᴇʀʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴘʀɪᴏʀ ᴛᴏ ꜰɪʀꜱᴛ ɢʀᴇᴇᴛɪɴɢ ɪꜱ ᴜᴘ ᴛᴏ ʟʟᴍ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴀᴄᴋɴᴏᴡʟᴇᴅɢᴇ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴛʀɪʙᴀʟ ᴄʜᴇꜰ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 112px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_19a9bfec-0999-4e82-9b2e-e6d0fac982de.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"67311507-a983-44e8-89c4-a6959d459395_92c30d3b-d8ab-4fdc-ac45-7d1b6f24feb1.webp","creator":"EminemsSalsa","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🪢 Scenario","👤 AnyPOV","😂 Comedy","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2595,"messages":25957,"created_at":"2024-07-04T15:08:19.866699+00:00"}